#. type: Content of: <ul><li><p>
msgid ""
"Spyware in many e-readers&mdash;not only the Kindle: <a href=\"https://www."
"eff.org/pages/reader-privacy-chart-2012\"> they report even which page the "
"user reads at what time</a>."
